# A cond-attr branch carrying BOTH a class leaf and an ordinary forced attr
# (aria-current): the class merges via the fold (root + spread + cond) AND
# aria-current renders on the taken branch (absent when untaken), proving the
# fold doesn't special-case away the branch's other attrs.
